fields.title: Bull Durham
fields.review: Crash Davis, a veteran catcher in baseball, is hired to coach Ebby Calvin 'Nuke' LaLoosh, a dim-witted beginner. However, both of them soon get involved with Annie, a groupie who loves the sport.

fields.title: Top Gun
fields.review: As students at the United States Navy's elite fighter weapons school compete to be best in the class, one daring young pilot learns a few things from a civilian instructor that are not taught in the classroom.

fields.title: Night at the Museum: Battle of the Smithsonian
fields.review: Larry Daley has to infiltrate the Smithsonian Institution to rescue Jedediah and Octavius after they are accidentally shipped there along with a few artefacts.

fields.title: Weathering with You
fields.review: In Tokyo, a runaway high school student facing financial struggles ends up with a job at a small-time publisher. One day, he meets a young girl who has the ability to control the weather.

fields.title: Mencuri Raden Saleh
fields.review: A group plans to steal a priceless historical painting 'The Arrest of Prince Diponegoro' by Raden Saleh from the Presidential Palace.

fields.title: Nope
fields.review: The residents of a lonely gulch in inland California bear witness to an uncanny and chilling discovery.

fields.title: Everything Everywhere All at Once
fields.review: An aging Chinese immigrant is swept up in an insane adventure, in which she alone can save the world by exploring other universes connecting with the lives she could have led.

fields.title: Doctor Strange in the Multiverse of Madness
fields.review: Doctor Strange teams up with a mysterious teenage girl from his dreams who can travel across multiverses, to battle multiple threats, including other-universe versions of himself, which threaten to wipe out millions across the multiverse. They seek help from Wanda the Scarlet Witch, Wong and others.

fields.title: Back to the Future
fields.review: Marty McFly, a 17-year-old high school student, is accidentally sent 30 years into the past in a time-traveling DeLorean invented by his close friend, the maverick scientist Doc Brown.

fields.title: The Shining
fields.review: A family heads to an isolated hotel for the winter where a sinister presence influences the father into violence, while his psychic son sees horrific forebodings from both past and future.
